Project Name: Simple DEX UI for XCP Tokens
Overview
This project is a proof-of-concept for a simple Decentralized Exchange (DEX) user interface for XCP tokens. The project aims to provide a user-friendly way to trade XCP tokens by listing available trading pairs, generating quotes, and facilitating transactions.

Features
Token Input: A text field where users can input the token they want to sell.
Available Pairs: A list of available trading pairs based on the input token.
Quote: A feature that calculates the cost of the transaction based on the selected trading pair and amount.
Order: A button that generates a QR code and transaction payload for the user to sign with their freewallet.
Market Check: A real-time check against unconfirmed transactions to prevent front-running.
Prerequisites
Node.js
npm or yarn
Git
